{"tid":1669134,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中國金雞獎公布入圍名單 港片零入圍(《紅海行動》除外)","createTime":"2019-10-22T11:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T12:14:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12a03f9deb691ffb76adc57a24e15af9b9a9f042","tid":1669134,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:18:03.000Z","msg":"中國金雞獎頒獎典禮刻意選在今年11月23日舉辦，撞期今年金馬獎。今金雞獎公布入圍名單，多項提名獎項的《後來的我們》、《我不是藥神》、《暴雪將至》、《老獸》等電影，多是先前獲得金馬提名的舊片，且細看影帝后入圍者，並沒有太多新的中國片出頭。再者，除了徐崢、白百何、周冬雨、姚晨等算是一線巨星，其實其他星光頗為黯淡。<br />\n<br />\n眾入圍者中，台灣影人僅有劉若英以導演《後來的我們》獲最佳故事片、影后、男配角、編劇等提名，但其實該片去年就獲得第55屆金馬獎包括最佳新導演、男配等5項提名。不過，香港電影今年被間接禁賽金馬獎，但包括《無雙》、《掃毒2》等中港合資作品，被視為中國出品，但也不被金雞獎青睞，連技術獎項都沒有，兩頭皆空。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20191022/1652547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191022%2F1652547%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=e27c7548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191022%2F1652547%2F&h=52400b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20191022/1652547/</a>"},{"pid":"e2d5b67af28ce05d4ae23b46529fa27ad70dda12","tid":1669134,"uid":28244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"鎖國算啦 垃圾獎 WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得理奶共狗先覺得好正好光榮"},{"pid":"0886b959469bfb95b408081e8d12b0ca5640fadb","tid":1669134,"uid":22218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"臭雞獎WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267eb9f4bf6d375bd2555f15add2f15553ca049a","tid":1669134,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d5b67af28ce05d4ae23b46529fa27ad70dda12","tid":1669134,"uid":28244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"鎖國算啦 垃圾獎 WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得理奶共狗先覺得好正好光榮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"諷刺在香港啲老闆為左奶共杯葛台灣，人哋又唔俾面你"},{"pid":"58251478c2aa70bc882e2909fe99c0d33ae9b235","tid":1669134,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"咪由得班支那狗打飛機囉<br />\n唔撚洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f487da02dfb27305ac94d9bffec046a08bc44478","tid":1669134,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}